Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:17.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(0,200)}那即是你的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:23.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(0,200)}过去？  未来？
